~~ A couple of integer math functions that all the interpreters will need to
~~ evaluate the expressions.

def 

~~ A factorial function
fac(i int) -> int/error :
    i < 0 :
        error "can't take the factorial of a negative number"
    i == 0 :
        1
    else : 
        i * fac i-1

~~ An exponential function.
exp(i, j int) -> int :
    j < 0 :
        error "can't take inverse exponents"
    j == 0 :
        1
    else :
        i * exp(i, j-1)
